{
  "Daily Note Header": {
    "scope": "markdown",
    "prefix": "daily",
    "body": [
      "# ${CURRENT_YEAR}-${CURRENT_MONTH}-${CURRENT_DATE}",
      "",
      "## 📅 今日计划",
      "- [ ] $1",
      "",
      "## 📝 笔记",
      "$2",
      "",
      "## 🎯 今日总结",
      "$3",
      "",
      "---",
      "**标签**: #日记 #${CURRENT_YEAR} #${CURRENT_MONTH}",
      "**创建时间**: ${CURRENT_YEAR}-${CURRENT_MONTH}-${CURRENT_DATE} ${CURRENT_HOUR}:${CURRENT_MINUTE}"
    ],
    "description": "创建日记笔记模板"
  },
  "Project Note": {
    "scope": "markdown",
    "prefix": "project",
    "body": [
      "# $1 项目笔记",
      "",
      "## 📋 项目概述",
      "- **项目名称**: $1",
      "- **开始时间**: ${CURRENT_YEAR}-${CURRENT_MONTH}-${CURRENT_DATE}",
      "- **负责人**: $2",
      "- **状态**: $3",
      "",
      "## 🎯 目标",
      "$4",
      "",
      "## 📊 进度跟踪",
      "- [ ] $5",
      "",
      "## 📝 会议纪要",
      "$6",
      "",
      "## 🔗 相关资源",
      "$7",
      "",
      "---",
      "**标签**: #项目 #$1",
      "**创建时间**: ${CURRENT_YEAR}-${CURRENT_MONTH}-${CURRENT_DATE}"
    ],
    "description": "创建项目笔记模板"
  },
  "Meeting Note": {
    "scope": "markdown", 
    "prefix": "meeting",
    "body": [
      "# $1 会议纪要",
      "",
      "## 📅 会议信息",
      "- **时间**: ${CURRENT_YEAR}-${CURRENT_MONTH}-${CURRENT_DATE} ${CURRENT_HOUR}:${CURRENT_MINUTE}",
      "- **参与人**: $2",
      "- **主持人**: $3",
      "",
      "## 📋 议程",
      "1. $4",
      "",
      "## 💡 讨论要点",
      "$5",
      "",
      "## ✅ 行动项",
      "- [ ] $6 (@$7 - $8)",
      "",
      "## 📄 附件",
      "$9",
      "",
      "---",
      "**标签**: #会议 #$1",
      "**下次会议**: $10"
    ],
    "description": "创建会议纪要模板"
  }
}